{"tid":89991,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"E-kids麥花臣演唱會即時報導","createTime":"2017-01-21T17:11:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-22T08:38:34.000Z","uid":22675,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fe13d992bad72bb081bbf0b1050764cdd826fd12","tid":89991,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T17:11:55.000Z","msg":"【MK Pop文化乜乜乜&hellip;】 <br />\n唱第3首已走上山頂觀眾席 E-kids咩玩法？ <br />\n<br />\n建立時間 (HKT): 0121 21:08 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170121/large/1485004010_0180.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170121%2Flarge%2F1485004010_0180.jpg&h=a57751db&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\nMK Pop始祖E-kids闊別N年重組、今晚假旺角麥花臣場館舉行「3XL演唱會」，喺晚上8點37分開場，3名成員阮民安（Tommy）、林詠倫（Alan）、郁禮賢（Tim，又名Kasa）分別以金、灰、紅色頭登場，3個人都係著白色T恤大樓，仲有女Dancers傍住出場，好有氣勢。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170121/large/1485004014_0302.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170121%2Flarge%2F1485004014_0302.jpg&h=98c64e15&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢哋先後以《Africa EDM》同《最佳表情》開場，現場反應好好，班觀眾高舉又揮動發光棒嚟打拍子。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170121/large/1485004012_634e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170121%2Flarge%2F1485004012_634e.jpg&h=d299f058&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唱到第3首《第一個唱》時，3個唱到走曬落台，同歌迷作近距離接觸，E-kids仲走上山頂觀眾席。到第4《魅力移動》時，E-kids返番上台，然後叫全場觀眾企起身，玩到好high咁。 <br />\n<br />\n而喺觀眾席度，除有有鄭世豪外，仲有E-kids舊同事裕美，以及見到「東方昇」同「專家Dickson」都有嚟睇。大會又喺台後螢光幕，播出當年E-kids出活動時，歌迷舉牌唱歌片段。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170121/large/1485007221_5c8b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170121%2Flarge%2F1485007221_5c8b.jpg&h=5e7ba66a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\nlink:<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170121/56205433\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170121%2F56205433&d=SsN2fCzZsuJIJ9cIHCIj4ZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=35c76b08\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170121%2F56205433&h=5e806338\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170121/56205433</a>"},{"pid":"b394357d57a92e1ddb42580aed27d7ecaa70ba85","tid":89991,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T17:12:27.000Z","msg":"Tim宣佈將做老竇 係咪要改名做E-Dads？ <br />\n<br />\n建立時間 (HKT): 0121 22:25 <br />\n<br />\n好喇好喇，終於嚟到E-kids騷尾二嗰part喇，佢哋又換咗衫，唱新歌《唱歌彈琴》，有4男4女dancers伴舞。其後開始唱別人的歌，先嚟草蜢首《好戲在後頭》，然後再到Tim獨唱周杰倫首《蝸牛》，喺呢個候，台後螢幕播出佢同老婆嘅結婚相，仲寫住「我們結婚了，還有，將會做爸爸」，博得全場觀眾大聲歡呼。 <br />\n<br />\n咦？咁橋嘅，Tommy仔早排被揭同女友張倚雯（Eva）秘密註冊結婚，Eva日前仲被《蘋果》影到佢個肚已經籮咁大&hellip;&hellip;咁E-kids咪即係會有兩個爸爸，咁要改名喇噃&hellip;&hellip;不如，就E-Dads？ <br />\n<br />\n返番入正題，Alan獨唱陳奕迅嗰隻《浮誇》，著住粉紅色毛毛長褸襯黑皮褲嘅佢，唱到後段仲除衫騷肌。 <br />\n<br />\nlink:<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170121/56205620\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170121%2F56205620&d=SsN2fCzZsuJIJ9cIHCIj4ZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=b463e4ea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170121%2F56205620&h=3c9d446d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170121/56205620</a>"},{"pid":"4b4ae4ff30c4727b5beb04f15ef88c14728ee4af","tid":89991,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T17:13:08.000Z","msg":"提BIGBANG騷耐未入場 Tommy：係咪轉咗軚過嚟？ <br />\n<br />\n建立時間 (HKT): 0121 21:20 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170121/large/1485005077_d6a1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170121%2Flarge%2F1485005077_d6a1.jpg&h=b64ecfc8&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n繼續睇MK Pop始祖E-kids個重組演唱會，喺第二部分，E-kids換咗衫，唱譚詠麟嗰首《玩出火》，佢哋3個邊跳邊唱；到唱《私人時段》，就同觀眾一齊大合唱，到大合唱完，E-kids同啲觀眾傾偈。 <br />\n<br />\nAlan：「好唔好睇？我哋排得好辛苦，好彩我哋賣飛前BIGBANG未賣。」 <br />\nTommy：「聽講排好耐都未入到場，係咪轉咗軚過嚟？好似話2點排到7點都未入得&hellip;&hellip;」 <br />\nTim：「我哋以前出活動，當我哋叫『We are'，你哋就會嗌E-kids&hellip;」 <br />\n然後台下觀眾就一齊跟住嗌E-kids。 <br />\n<br />\n現場啲fans反應好好，聽快歌時企曬起身，到唱慢歌，好似《再見4.1》嗰陣，就乖乖哋坐低曬揮棒，好冧豬咁！仲有歌迷送花畀Tim。 <br />\n<br />\nlink:<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170121/56205470\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170121%2F56205470&d=SsN2fCzZsuJIJ9cIHCIj4ZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=0209717b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170121%2F56205470&h=b9b56a16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170121/56205470</a>"},{"pid":"9b4ae64b21173f8395eb6266113d69851fc7cd43","tid":89991,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T17:13:30.000Z","msg":"Alan唱「眼鼻唇」 Tommy被金毛女摷到「好肉緊」 <br />\n<br />\n建立時間 (HKT): 0121 22:05 <br />\n<br />\nMK Pop始祖E-kids個重組演唱會話咁快就嚟到第3部份，佢哋以《赤壁之戰》打頭陣，Tim有solo跳舞環節，佢著全套紅色軍服現身。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170121/large/1485007121_e27d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170121%2Flarge%2F1485007121_e27d.jpg&h=78b83a17&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n繼喺上一part MC部份抽同樣係今日開騷嘅BIGBANG水，話人哋嗰邊要排隊等入場外，佢哋仲唱埋出口，先有Alan唱唱太陽首《eyes nose lips》幾句，先到佢獨唱自己嘅《I dare you》。 <br />\n<br />\n之後輪到幾年前抄過BIGBANG隊長G-Dragon而成為話題人物嘅Tommy，佢先唱老翻GD首《Crayon》嘅《踩唔死我》，有廿幾個dancers幫佢伴舞，仲個個金髮，襯番金毛Tommy，成堆女dancers仲一齊伸出「魔爪」&hellip;&hellip;摸向Tommy肉體，Tommy好肉緊&hellip;&hellip;咁唱，之後再唱咗佢首《一世朋友》（幾句咁多）。最後佢唱埋隻《玩玩具》，solo部份就完曬。 <br />\n<br />\nlink:<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170121/56205522\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170121%2F56205522&d=SsN2fCzZsuJIJ9cIHCIj4ZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=f490ae79\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170121%2F56205522&h=1000fe48\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170121/56205522</a>"},{"pid":"abcd80ddf20aea8f4a92d25f35ddd44c07c6cd7d","tid":89991,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T17:13:51.000Z","msg":"E-kids做一百分演唱會 <br />\nAlan：我呢幾日瞓唔夠10個鐘 <br />\n<br />\n建立時間 (HKT): 0122 00:00 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170121/large/1485012168_1fca.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170121%2Flarge%2F1485012168_1fca.jpg&h=04b83f3b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n終於嚟到E-kids重組演唱會最後一部份，佢哋再度擔度出場，今次係藍禮服襯黑褲，唱《青春變魔術》、《倉鼠俱樂部》，又安排咗一班小朋友伴舞，唱完之後，Alan問隊友「o依家點？」，跟住又叫Tommy講啲嘢，因為「你係骨幹嚟㗎嘛！」 <br />\n<br />\nTommy就話：「咁多年嚟，E-kids同香港都發生咗好多事，所以咗啲歌好代表到。」然後佢哋就唱出Supper Moment嘅《無盡》，同吳雨霏嘅《愛是最大權利》。 <br />\n<br />\n而喺唱最後一首歌《青春火花》前，3個先喺台上講感受，Tim話：「為咗今次我哋做足100分，呢幾日我瞓唔夠10個鐘，終於將MK pop演唱會帶嚟俾大家。」Alan就即刻話:「你瞓咗10個鐘，我喺屋企瞓咗幾年都無嘢做。」然後就唱歌，仲走落台同觀眾攬攬合照，然後完場，但全場觀眾大叫Encore。 <br />\n<br />\n三個出台前螢幕播林海峰當日喺咤吒講樂壇小強嗰段，然後3個先再出場，三個再出嚟唱《開始戀愛》，唱完捉台下嘅東方昇同Dickson傾偈，問佢哋覺得今晚點？Dickson:「100分」，之後再問同毛記分獎禮比較呢？東方昇:「梗係你哋啦。」之後喺台上多謝品牌借衫畀佢哋，話自己唔係奀星，係濕星，都竟然肯借衫俾佢哋，之後唱埋《初哥》就完騷。 <br />\n<br />\nlink:<a href=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170121/large/1485012168_1fca.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170121%2Flarge%2F1485012168_1fca.jpg&d=SsN2fCzZsuJIJ9cIHCIj4ZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=c66ef82c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170121%2Flarge%2F1485012168_1fca.jpg&h=38ae5cf2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170121/large/1485012168_1fca.jpg</a>"},{"pid":"1f1ace91503560b494a9470acffb1b01c5c9860a","tid":89991,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T17:14:29.000Z","msg":"E-Kids旺角騷 重現佔旺片段 <br />\n<br />\n建立時間 (HKT): 0122 00:05 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170121/large/1485012325_6d6b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170121%2Flarge%2F1485012325_6d6b.jpg&h=693aa7ab&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\nMK Pop嘅嘢，你真係估佢唔到，就好似MK仔一樣，佢哋做嘅嘢，往往令你震驚。就好似噚晚E-Kids喺旺角麥花球場開個唱咁，到Tommy阮民安獨唱《差一點我們會飛》 (電影《哪一天我們會飛》主題曲)嘅時候，螢幕播出佔領運動片段，包括佔旺同佔鐘，有7個著教會聖詩班打扮嘅伴唱。 <br />\n<br />\n唔係「今天我」，《哪一天》的歌詞還需細嚼，例如「仍然要相信 這裡會有想像 求時間變慢 不想迫於成長 未了願 我替你朝浪濤吶喊 聽聽有沒有被迴響 青春怎會零創傷」，但環顧現今，除咗達明，有冇人會播佔領片段？就好似講真話咁，依家只要有人講真話，就已經可以將之封神封聖。即如，有香港電視台曾以節目全用繁體字係selling point一樣。 <br />\n<br />\n香港好病。 <br />\n<br />\nlink:<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170122/56205656\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170122%2F56205656&d=SsN2fCzZsuJIJ9cIHCIj4ZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=d46d5be2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170122%2F56205656&h=161cab6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170122/56205656</a>"},{"pid":"e7843c1c0a61ae5c7b54ae1580d89b62ef2fc7b5","tid":89991,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T18:35:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86f732a545874638f91e264607bfb38db8408747","tid":89991,"uid":37281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T20:55:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2316db56db509496797381b633b4d4513f1f5dfc","tid":89991,"uid":33463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T21:09:40.000Z","msg":"呢隊野代表到香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好過垃圾bigbang<br />\n無論樣，聲，服式，歲數完全屌打bigbang<br />\n投放多d資金落e-kids應該會紅過bigbang<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10dc2dd582575c2fcc18aa4cce147c7c9322ba86","tid":89991,"uid":807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T21:14:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4edf405db9144bdf630392d5bc47997cde73f86","tid":89991,"uid":9566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T21:42:40.000Z","msg":"正式上神檯"},{"pid":"631f76024f1e83b9c25c8e516664187938e11789","tid":89991,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T01:01:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a2a89da3383c6561308f13daf3092961d6c31567","tid":89991,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T01:20:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7afada77351706b0df0cde2f35814bca1e194a8e","tid":89991,"uid":57797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T01:20:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢隊野代表到香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好過垃圾bigbang<br />\n無論樣，聲，服式，歲數完全屌打bigbang<br />\n投放多d資金落e-kids應該會紅過bigbang<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmo